file   | bind//named.conf.logging                 | /etc/bind/named.conf.logging                 | 644  | root:bind  | none   | none | "Настройка логирования"                                          | AUTHOR|LAST_MODIFIED|QUERIESLOG_DNS
file   | bind//resolv.conf                        | /etc/resolv.conf                             | 644  | root:root  | none   | +i   | "Системный резолвер"                                             | AUTHOR|LAST_MODIFIED|LOCAL_DOMAIN
